---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Hana Code Corp"
  description="Privacy Policy for Hana Code Corp and its applications."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="section hero">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="effective">Effective Date: March 1, 2026</p>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Hana Code Corp ("we," "our," or "us") is a software company based in
          Calgary, Alberta, Canada. We are committed to protecting your privacy
          and being transparent about how we handle your information. This
          Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information
          when you use our applications and services, including Slackwater.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          Our applications are designed with privacy in mind. The information we
          collect depends on which app you use:
        </p>
        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Slackwater</h3>
            <p>
              Financial planning inputs you provide (account balances, income,
              retirement age preferences, contribution amounts). This data is
              used solely to generate your retirement projections and is stored
              locally on your device wherever possible.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Account Information</h3>
            <p>
              If you create an account, we collect your email address to provide
              account functionality and communicate with you about our services.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Usage Analytics</h3>
            <p>
              We may collect anonymized usage data to understand how our apps are
              used and to improve the experience. This data does not personally
              identify you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and maintain our applications and services</li>
          <li>Generate financial projections and retirement planning calculations</li>
          <li>Improve and optimize our apps based on usage patterns</li>
          <li>Respond to your questions and support requests</li>
          <li>Send important updates about our services when necessary</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third
          parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take the security of your data seriously. Financial planning data in
          Slackwater is stored locally on your device wherever possible. When
          data is transmitted, it is encrypted in transit using
          industry-standard TLS encryption.
        </p>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to
          protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration,
          disclosure, or destruction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          Our apps may use third-party services for functionality such as
          analytics and crash reporting. These services have their own privacy
          policies. Third-party services we may use include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Apple App Store (for app distribution and in-app purchases)</li>
          <li>Analytics services (for anonymized usage data)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our applications are not directed at children under the age of 13. We
          do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we
          become aware that we have collected information from a child under 13,
          we will take steps to delete that information promptly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          In accordance with Canadian privacy law (PIPEDA) and applicable
          provincial legislation, you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:hana@cousins.ai">hana@cousins.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make
          changes, we will update the "Effective Date" at the top of this page
          and, where appropriate, notify you through our applications. We
          encourage you to review this policy periodically.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our
          data practices, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Hana Code Corp</strong><br />
          Calgary, Alberta, Canada<br />
          <a href="mailto:hana@cousins.ai">hana@cousins.ai</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .effective {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .card:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .feature {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: 4rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
